title: Dizzy Don Comics # 22 (F.E. Howard Publications)
description:
Continues from The Funny Comics #1-20
Two issues of this book came out, i only got one, and i couldn't really find anything about it on the internet, other thant it's published in 1946 and probably in Canada

Still, this is a pretty cool detective comic with very unusual artwork by one Manny Eason, which is more remiscent of an alternative comic from the early 90's

Kinda primitive and kinda forward of it's time too

Published by F.E. Howard Publications 1946
52 pages
